Gender Pay Report 2018

A message from
your CEO.

As CEO, having an environment 
of fairness and equality at 
Pattonair is high on my agenda. 

Due to this, I welcome the government’s initiative for companies to publish their 
Gender pay gaps as it’s a positive step towards reducing the gender pay gap.

