The main driver for this gap is the proportion of females in senior roles compared to males, which 
is traditionally typical of our industry, and is not driven by pay inequality. It is my aim to push our 
companies ambition to create an inclusive culture, bringing gender balance into our workforce. 
Whilst we are making progress already, the report shows that there is still work to do in this area.

This will take time, but I believe that this can be achieved through our recruitment initiatives and 
talent development that attracts and develops a diverse workforce, whilst supporting career 
