What we have done so far.

• Our grading and benchmarking process ensures

consistency of like for like and similar roles.

• 66% of our 2017 interns brought

into the business were female

• We have recruited females into several key senior

roles over recent years, including Head
of Quality and HR Director

What we are planning.

• We are in the process of implementing a

new HR system that will provide us with better
analytics to identify key focus areas.

• We are working with our managers to identify talent

and support their development and career progression.

• We will continue to explore ways of attracting females

into our industry through our enhanced
recruitment processes.

